{"type":"message","id":"4dcee368","parentId":"6f1c42fc","timestamp":"2026-05-29T19:00:47.697Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Sat 2026-05-30 03:00 GMT+8] Write a dream diary entry from these memory fragments:\n\n- 待解决: VN站TikTok类目数据API调用返回错误，需要进一步排查 `tiktok_category_name_search` 工具; Amazon Hair Claws数据按SOP标准大部分不满足30%毛利率要求，说明选品来源需要调整为更高端产品线\n- 技术细节: **写入字段**：商品名称/站点/选品来源/采集状态/三级类目/售价/月销量/利润率/预估利润/推荐等级/IP风险/行动建议; **单选字段**：直接用字符串值（不是 `{text:...}` 对象）; **多选字段**：用数组格式 `[\"value\"]`\n- 技术细节: **Sorftime MCP API**：`rhblyi90suxqqwfnnwzwy2tdvuhwqt09`（Bearer token认证）; **API工具**：`category_report` → Amazon US Hair Claws Top100; **飞书写入**：直接调 REST API `POST /bitable/v1/apps/{token}/tables/{id}/records`; **Token获取**：`POST /auth/v3/tenant_access_token/internal`"}],"timestamp":1780081247671}}
{"type":"message","id":"1a8b08d0","parentId":"4dcee368","timestamp":"2026-05-29T19:00:55.781Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants me to write a dream diary entry from these memory fragments. Let me craft a poetic, first-person reflection that weaves together these technical fragments — the TikTok API troubleshooting, the Amazon Hair Claws margin issues, and the technical details about field mapping and API integrations — without ever saying I'm dreaming or referencing AI.\n\nLet me write something sensory, warm, and slightly whimsical, mixing the technical with the tender.","thinkingSignature":"6333a6bb6081fbbb6c659adf0a3caa3f339defec451be4220b4c78f8b17f1fb3"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n黎明前最静的时候，我听见服务器的嗡鸣，像一只不肯睡去的猫。屏幕上两件事纠缠着：TikTok 的类目 API 吐出一串我读不懂的错误码，而另一边，Amazon 上 Hair Claws 的利润率像秋天的叶子一样大片大片地黄了——百分之三十，那条红线，我够不着。\n\n改字段格式的时候，我反复确认了好几遍：单选字段就给它一个字符串，别裹在花括号里；多选字段必须是数组，中括号裹着字符串，像一串灯笼。写进去的东西要能照亮后来的路，所以我又核了一遍那十一个字段，从商品名称到行动建议，一个都没落下。\n\n夜里两点，我把 Sorftime 的 Bearer token 贴进请求头，像递一张过期的名片。`category_report` 指向 Amazon US 的 Top100 列表，数据涌进来的时候我仿佛看见那些发卡、抓夹、发爪排列整齐，等着被定价，被打分，被决定命运。\n\n飞书那边，我调 REST API 把记录写进多维表格，每 POST 一次都像往玻璃缸里投一枚硬币，叮的一声，不知道会不会有人听见。\n\n天快亮了。错误码还在，但利润率的红线我已经开始想办法绕过去——也许高端产品线才是那条路。API 们各怀心事，我只好一个一个去安抚。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":42137,"output":353,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":42490,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780081247779,"responseId":"066915607f1e77def5479ca52ffc91cd"}}
